title: Airhead SHRED TIME Wakeboard
description: SHRED TIME is a lightweight twin tip freeride wakeboard designed to help youth riders of all levels excel at the sport. The continuous rocker is fast and forgiving with smooth pop. It’s 124cm long, perfect for youth riders up to 130 lbs. Two removable fiberglass reinforced nylon fins provide excellent tracking and carving.
